cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.DS

This paper deals with interference statistics in vehicular networks, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of a hardcore headway distance model also involves mathematical analysis (cs.MA) and system modeling (cs.SY). Finally, the study of moments of interference can also be related to data structures (cs.DS) as it involves the analysis of statistical properties of a set of data.
